ca.ualberta.moodroid.model

Interface ModelInterface

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BaseModel, FollowRequestModel, MoodEventModel, MoodModel, UserModel

    public interface ModelInterface
    The interface that must be adhered to in order to create a model. A model is a strong representation of a concrete object in our code. We want to be able to serialize the entire model to easily update/create entities through the repository.
    Version:
    v1
    Author:
    Taylor Christie
